longBusinessSummary: Canoe Mining Ventures Corp. engages in the acquisition, exploration, evaluation, and development of gold resource properties in Northern Ontario, Canada. It holds a 100% interest in the Kerrs gold property consisting of 12 mining leasehold patents located in the Larder Lake Mining Division of Ontario. The company was incorporated in 2011 and is based in Toronto, Canada.
